Package file_handling.interfaces

Interface IJsonProcessor

All Superinterfaces:
IFileProcessor
All Known Implementing Classes:
JsonProcessor
public interface IJsonProcessor
extends IFileProcessor
Interface defining JSON-specific processing operations. Extends IFileProcessor to combine general file processing with JSON capabilities.
